{"parse":{"title":"Golden Darter","pageid":98180,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|itemid=27438\n|stack=20\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_36\n|quality=Common\n|name=Golden Darter\n|ilvl=60\n|sell={{cost|||8}}\n}}</onlyinclude>\n'''Golden Darter''' are used to make {{loot|common|Golden Fish Sticks}} and are found in the rivers and lakes of [[Terokkar Forest]] and [[Zangarmarsh]].\n<br />\nThey can occasionally be found in Brackish Mixed Schools in the lakes of [[Zangarmarsh]]:\n*[[Umbrafen Lake]]\n*[[The Lagoon]]\n*[[Serpent Lake]]\n*[[Marshlight Lake]]\n\nThey are more commonly fished from Highland Mixed Pools along with {{loot|common|Furious Crawdad}}. These pools can be found in the elevated lakes of [[Terokkar Forest]]:\n*[[Lake Ere'Noru]]\n*[[Lake Jorune]]\n*[[Blackwind Lake]]\n<br />\nThese are required for [[Golden Fish Sticks]].\n\n== Patch changes ==\n{{Patch 2.0.1|note=Added in [[Burning Crusade]].}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|27438}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/golden_darter.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]"}}}